2. Why CPUs Still Matter (in 2026)
Niche coins: Certain coins (like Monero) use CPUâ€‘friendly algorithms that resist ASIC domination.
Low entry cost: Used CPUs or older server chips may allow small miners to enter without huge GPU/ASIC investments. (Reddit)
